attachmentHtml:
PC Number: 2014-0556

Date: 2014-05-09

The Committee of the Privy Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Justice, advises that Darryl J. Brown, of the City of Regina, in the Province of Saskatchewan, Barrister-at-law, be appointed a Judge of Her Majesty's Court of Queen's Bench for Saskatchewan.


Sur recommandation du ministre de la Justice, le Comité du Conseil privé recommande que Darryl J. Brown, de la ville de Regina dans la province de la Saskatchewan, avocat, soit nommé juge de la Cour du Banc de la Reine de la Saskatchewan.
